The Payment Gateway is an integral part of any e-Commerce business. It enables the site to accept payment and realize
the value of the payment. The payment gateway creates a unique Transaction Id and securely handles all payment related
information as per the PCI-DSS 2.0 norms.

1. It keeps a record in active search for a period of 6 months and then archives the transaction.
2. All transactions are reversible as per the terms and conditions set by PCI-DSS v2.0
3. All transactions that are carried out by this payment gateway are completely Atomic and follow CRUD principles. 

